restlib

Class ResponseWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • restlib.Response
      • restlib.ResponseWrapper

  • @Immutable
public class ResponseWrapper
extends Response
    An implementation of Response which forwards all its method calls to another instance of Response. Subclasses should override one or more methods to modify the behavior of the backing Response as desired per the decorator pattern.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Modifier Constructor and Description
      protected ResponseWrapper(Response delegate)
      Constructs an instance of ResponseWrapper that forwards all method calls to delegate.
